		<title>狗狗和貓咪誰更懂「鏡子裡的自己」？答案超出想像！</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/21/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e5%92%8c%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e8%aa%b0%e6%9b%b4%e6%87%82%e3%80%8c%e9%8f%a1%e5%ad%90%e8%a3%a1%e7%9a%84%e8%87%aa%e5%b7%b1%e3%80%8d%ef%bc%9f%e7%ad%94%e6%a1%88%e8%b6%85%e5%87%ba%e6%83%b3/</link>
		
